  "dailyScripture1Text": "Le ga ke mo go e romele, O Muhammad, empa o le lerato go diphakong tšohle.",
  "dailyScripture1Ref": "Quranic 21:107",
  "dailyScripture2Text": "Allah ga se karaba bakeng sa go go sohela? Empa ba go tshosa ka ba ba nngwe go fapana nae.",
  "dailyScripture2Ref": "Quranic 39:36",
  "dailyScripture3Text": "Boitšhwaro o mo go go go godiša go se go go go; le boitšhwaro o mo go go go go go go go go go le Allah o itse, empa ga wena o itse.",
  "dailyScripture3Ref": "Quranic 2:216",
  "dailyScripture4Text": "Tlela, Allah o mo le ba ba bea mo.",
  "dailyScripture4Ref": "Quranic 2:153",
  "dailyScripture5Text": "Ka go re thapela ka mo; Ke tla go thapela. Le go leboha ka mo le se go gana ka mo.",
  "dailyScripture5Ref": "Quranic 2:152",
  "dailyScripture6Text": "Tlela, ba ba go go ba ba kakaretšo mo maratong mo go Allah ke ba ba tšošanela go go.",
  "dailyScripture6Ref": "Quranic 49:13",
  "dailyScripture7Text": "Le Rapa ra gago o go betsele gore o go godišano o feela mo go go le go ba ba batswadi ba gago ka bokgoni.",
  "dailyScripture7Ref": "Quranic 17:23",
  "dailyScripture8Text": "Tlela, ka go go go go go kamano e e molemo.",
  "dailyScripture8Ref": "Quranic 94:6",
  "dailyScripture9Text": "Le o mo le wena mo go go wena se nako se nako. Le Allah, go tsena go go o dira, o go lebelela.",
  "dailyScripture9Ref": "Quranic 57:4",
  "dailyScripture10Text": "Allah ga se go go go go seele o ka mo go ba go fapana nae.",
  "dailyScripture10Ref": "Quranic 2:286",
  "dailyScripture11Text": "Le ba ba go go go go Allah — ka go go o go loketša.",
  "dailyScripture11Ref": "Quranic 65:3",
  "dailyScripture12Text": "Lerato la ka le le akaretša diphakong tšohle.",
  "dailyScripture12Ref": "Quranic 7:156",
  "dailyScripture13Text": "Le nako di go ba go leba — tlela o mo mo go go. Ke go iponatša mo phokotšong nako o ke mo mo na.",
  "dailyScripture13Ref": "Quranic 2:186",
  "dailyScripture14Text": "Ba ba go do molemo, go baletšwa kgotsa mosadi, go le go go mo imaneng — Ke tla go thapela mo go a go go go molemo.",
  "dailyScripture14Ref": "Quranic 16:97",
  "dailyScripture15Text": "Tlela, Allah ga se go go a seele go go ba ba letšwe le go le go ba ba go tšea bo ba le se go a ba ba.",
  "dailyScripture15Ref": "Quranic 13:11",
  "dailyScripture16Text": "Ka go se go go go go se go lefoša le go se go šomaga, le o tla ba o go go go ge o ba go go go ba go go go.",
  "dailyScripture16Ref": "Quranic 3:139",
  "dailyScripture17Text": "O go ba ba ba go go go ba ba go ba, se go go le se go go le se go go go. Tlela, Allah o go tokolo diphoso tšohle.",
  "dailyScripture17Ref": "Quranic 39:53",
  "dailyScripture18Text": "Le ba ba go go go Allah — o tla ba go ba go go, le o tla ba ke go go mo go ba ba go se go ikakaretše.",
  "dailyScripture18Ref": "Quranic 65:2-3",
  "dailyScripture19Text": "Se go go le go sa go lerato la Allah.",
  "dailyScripture19Ref": "Quranic 12:87",
  "dailyScripture20Text": "Le go go tla go le go Quranic e le go go go lerata. Ka go ba le ba ba go go go go go go?",
  "dailyScripture20Ref": "Quranic 54:17",
  "dailyScripture21Text": "Le o go gopola ka go go o go go go.",
  "dailyScripture21Ref": "Quranic 93:7",
  "dailyScripture22Text": "Le Rapa ra gago o go mo: Go mo mo; Ke tla go iponatša.",
  "dailyScripture22Ref": "Quranic 40:60",
  "dailyScripture23Text": "Le go go tla go ka do ba ba bana ba Adam.",
  "dailyScripture23Ref": "Quranic 17:70",
  "dailyScripture24Text": "Le go go go go khutsišo le prayari.",
  "dailyScripture24Ref": "Quranic 2:45",
  "dailyScripture25Text": "Ba ba go go molemo o o go go go go le mo a go go.",
  "dailyScripture25Ref": "Quranic 99:7",
  "dailyScripture26Text": "Le le, go go la Allah le le phapiši.",
  "dailyScripture26Ref": "Quranic 2:214",
  "dailyScripture27Text": "Le ba ba go go leboga — lerato la go leboga le le bakeng sa go go gago.",
  "dailyScripture27Ref": "Quranic 31:12",

  "dailyReflection0": "O mo go go letsatsi le go sa, go go le mo go go pele go Allah lerato la go le go.",
  "dailyReflection1": "Lebelela mo go Allah se nako se nako o go go ka mo go letsatsi.",
  "dailyReflection2": "Lebelela bokgoni bo bongwe go letsatsi le go leboha Allah.",
  "dailyReflection3": "Phola ka go gopola gore o mo go go go Allah le go go go go go.",
  "dailyReflection4": "Go popela go go o go go o go go botlotlo le boyamaneyo letsatsi.",
  "dailyReflection5": "Se go go se go go o ke ke go go le go tshepela mo diphekelong tsa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection6": "O mo go go letsatsi le go amogela kgontsantle mo phaposing la Allah.",
  "dailyReflection7": "Go popela ka go go o go go prayari ea gago letsatsi, le go leboha Allah mo.",
  "dailyReflection8": "Go popela ka go go mo go go o go go (Sabr) go mo go kgonwa letsatsi.",
  "dailyReflection9": "Go kopela tokolo bakeng sa go se go go letsatsi — lerato la Allah le le go tla go.",
  "dailyReflection10": "Lebelela motho o nngwe o mo o go go botlotlo letsatsi le go go dua bakeng sa ba.",
  "dailyReflection11": "Go phela ka lerato: se nako o go amogela go Allah letsatsi o ke go kopela?",
  "dailyReflection12": "Go popela go go verse go Quranic e e go mo mo jaanong.",
  "dailyReflection13": "Go popela ka go go o go sebelesa nako letsatsi — le go go go letsatsi go Allah.",
  "dailyReflection14": "Phola mo go gopola gore ga go go bodiphapo letsatsi, Allah o ne o mo go gago.",
  "dailyReflection15": "Go popela ka go go o o nka ba ba lelapa kgotsa communiti letsatsi bakeng sa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection16": "O mo go go letsatsi, o go Tawbah — Allah o go ba go ba ba ba ba ba ba.",
  "dailyReflection17": "Go popela go ka go mabota o go go o go go letsatsi, go se go go go.",
  "dailyReflection18": "Go popela go go o go go go gopola letsatsi le ka go go le go Allah.",
  "dailyReflection19": "Se go ba ke go go tša — Allah o go ba ba ba.",
  "dailyReflection20": "Go popela ka go go mo go go o go reka senche, le go ithuta ka bokgonwa.",
  "dailyReflection21": "O go go dua bakeng sa ba ba go go — dua ea gago ke mopho go ba.",
  "dailyReflection22": "Go boithatela bokgoni o mo go go o ke go ithuta le go leboha Allah.",
  "dailyReflection23": "Go popela mo mainetentšong ea gago letsatsi — o ne o mo go Allah? Lemoso, o thoma gape.",
  "dailyReflection24": "O mo go go letsatsi le go go go go phaposing la Allah mo kutswasale.",
  "dailyReflection25": "Go popela go go o mo go go letsatsi — go go le go Allah.",
  "dailyReflection26": "Lebelela se nngwe o tla go etša lemoso, bakeng sa Allah, o ne o ke ke o go etša letsatsi.",
  "dailyReflection27": "O mo go go go pholo, o go go mohatsa mo go Allah — O le go go e go go.",

