  "disclaimerTitle": "Ka go go taelo ya apiki",
  "disclaimerBody": "Ayara e fana ka Islamic ponahalo, diphasatisi, le mabaka a go go go go go go mo go gago. Mabaka a a go fapela go boitsebiso le go go feela.\n\nAyara ga se go go seithuti se se go go.\nTaelo mo apiki ye ga se go go go go Islamic scholar, imam, mufti, kgotsa morutabuti o o tlagantswe go go. Ge o na le dipotšišo ka sehlapa sa Islamic, halal le haram maele, kgotsa go go go tšea, gopela go go mobo go go botshabelo mo komuniting ea gago.\n\nApiki ye ga se go go go go sehlapa.\nAyara ga se go etša go go go go dikgetsi ka fiqh (Islamic jurisprudence) kgotsa go go go tšea. Se nako se se lokela go go fatwa kgotsa go go go sehlapa.\n\nScholar go go go go bo.\nIslam e na le go go go ditraditional, disentre tša go go go (madhabs), le dikgonwa tša scholar. Mabaka mo apiki ye a tsena go go le se tla go laetšwa traditional e nngwe le nngwe.\n\nCommuniti e a boka.\nApiki ye e lebela go go go go mo go go tradisional empa go go bohlokwa ba mo ga imam, le go go go bajanala. Re leka go o go go le go ithuta go go seithuti se se nneng mo gago.",
  "disclaimerClose": "Ke utologa",
  "disclaimerInfoTooltip": "Ka go go taelo ya apiki",
  "disclaimerSettingsSubtitle": "Bakeng sa boitsebiso go feela. Phokoletsa go bala disclaimer e kakaretšo.",
  "disclaimerSectionHeader": "Taelo disclaimer"
}